    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>macaroni</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>macaroni</strong> for 6-7 min or until cooked with a bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>macaroni</strong> reserving 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[195ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml] </span><strong>starchy pasta water</strong> and set aside until later, reserve the pot</p>",
