      "instruction": "<p>While the pasta is cooking, peel and finely chop your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> with your<strong> ground sumac</strong>, 1/3 of your <strong>grated cheese </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> – this your <strong>sumac crumb</strong></p>",
