    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>roasted butternut squash </strong>to the <strong>harissa</strong> <strong>béchamel sauce</strong> with the <strong>drained macaroni </strong>and stir everything together – this is your <strong>mac 'n' cheese mixture</strong></p><p>Transfer the <strong>mac 'n' cheese mixture</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over the<strong> sumac crumb </strong>and put the dish in the oven for 10 min or until golden and bubbling – this is your <strong>harissa mac 'n' cheese</strong></p>",
